return (function () { if (phase) { do { x1 = 2.0 * Math.random() - 1.0; x2 = 2.0 * Math.random() - 1.0; w = x1 * x1 + x2 * x2; } while (w >= 1.0); w = Math.sqrt((-2.0 * Math.log(w)) / w); return x1 * w;
